item.title: Gabrielle Union
item.description: This week, Kevin Harts sits down with actor, businesswoman, and friend Gabrielle Union. They discuss Gab's legendary acting career and business ventures and give us a behind-the-scenes look at their friendship. Keep an eye out for her upcoming Netflix romantic comedy, The Perfect Find, and her BET Plus special, Gabrielle Union: My Journey to 50. Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/ijknOKeU

item.title: Career Boredom: How to Make Your Work Interesting Again | E103 Carla Fowler
item.description:
I remember being on fire for the first few years of my career. I was learning so much and every day brought a novel problem to solve.

Boredom wasn’t even a thought. I didn’t quite understand why people felt stale in their careers.


And then things started to slow. What was once a unique puzzle to solve, turned into an ongoing job responsibility. My job was filled with less learning and more…work... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/tsir/
